CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 22, 1945 reads: "Yuletide Spirit - Left: Yvonne Hall, comely college co-ed, pauses to appreciate the "Christmasy" atmosphere amid the picturesque decorations in the lobby of the Centre Avenue YMCA. The background depicts the journey of the Three Wise Men of old on their way to Bethlehem to present gifts to the Holy Child. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Yvonne Hall wearing long dark robe with light colored hood, seated on table next to mural of the "Three Wise Men" in lobby of Centre Avenue YMCA
